WEBVTT

00:11:59.925 --> 00:12:03.131
A boy named Jacob Atem

00:12:03.131 --> 00:12:06.326
had a different chance, but not before he experienced

00:12:06.326 --> 00:12:08.418
terribly tragedy.

00:12:08.418 --> 00:12:10.882
He watched — this is in Sudan —

00:12:10.882 --> 00:12:13.176
as his village — he was only seven years old —

00:12:13.176 --> 00:12:15.558
burned to the ground, and he learned

00:12:15.558 --> 00:12:17.397
that his mother and his father

00:12:17.397 --> 00:12:19.386
and his entire family

00:12:19.386 --> 00:12:21.250
were killed that day.

00:12:21.250 --> 00:12:23.040
Only his cousin survived, and the two of them

00:12:23.040 --> 00:12:25.320
walked for seven months —

00:12:25.320 --> 00:12:27.170
this is boys like him —

00:12:27.170 --> 00:12:30.378
chased and pursued by wild
animals and armed gangs,